properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St. Augustine FL out 20 NM; Waters from Fernandina Beach to St. Augustine FL from 20 to 60 NM; Waters from Altamaha Sound GA to Fernandina Beach FL from 20 to 60 NM; Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 29 at 1:45AM EST until January 31 at 1:00AM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 20 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 5 to 7 feet expected.

* WHERE...All Southeast Georgia coastal waters from Altamaha
Sound GA to Fernandina Beach FL out to 60 NM and Coastal
waters from Fernandina Beach FL to St Augustine FL out to 60
NM.

* WHEN...From 1 AM Thursday to 1 AM EST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 1 AM THURSDAY TO 1 AM EST FRIDAY
